Package: weathercan2
Title: Download and Format Weather Data from Environment and Climate Change Canada
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Your",
           family = "Name",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "your.email@example.com")
Description: Download historical weather data from Environment and Climate Change Canada (ECCC)
    using the MSC GeoMet API. Provides functions to search for weather stations and download
    daily, hourly, and monthly weather observations.
